data.description: Assumable VA Loan at 2.75%. Welcome to your dream entertaining home in Continental Reserve! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts a prime location with picturesque views & sunsets of Sombrero Peak. Enjoy the serene backdrop from your backyard pool and spa oasis. Nestled in this sought-after community, once you step inside this meticulously upgraded home, where oversized wood look tile floors set the stage for a perfect blend of elegance and functionality. The kitchen showcases white cabinets complemented by stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Every corner of this home is adorned with extra details and decorative touches, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. 1st floor bedroom with full bathroom, great option for multi-generational living.
